title: Grad school entrance exam registration begins (Beijing Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Beijing Municipal Government ) The 2016 national master's examination registration began on Saturday and will last until the end of October, the Beijing Youth Daily reported. Data from the Education Bureau shows 1.64 million people
